{"tid":1185816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六四名詞（三）歷史教訓","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T13:37:17.000Z","uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49867887de0699cd51af8177c49119b152278983","tid":1185816,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"<code>節錄</code><br />\n國家要生，個人要讓路。這個邏輯沒有改變。我們不認同。<span style=\"color: red;\">而每年悼念六四的人，若反而加強了國家的不可抵抗</span>、悲劇的宿命感，繼續「事大」，不講究自己和地方的尊嚴重，<span style=\"color: red;\">連愛國、愛哪一個國這種嚴肅的事情都淪為政治避險的工具</span>，那些晚上都是浪費的。以政客在香港的政治實踐來看 (事大主義、不信任抗爭者、自己時常都認同主權就是大過人權、不省察中華文化的霸權陰暗面)，<span style=\"color: red;\">有哪一處有繼承到任何前人的精神？</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vocus.cc/indiehongkong/5cf66453fd89780001a1e38c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvocus.cc%2Findiehongkong%2F5cf66453fd89780001a1e38c&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgqarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=75f9bb9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://vocus.cc/indiehongkong/5cf66453fd89780001a1e38c</a>"},{"pid":"b908548e02465145eb13c67de54abe30964f255d","tid":1185816,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9319098ad6b4d6a7de52423503ec3f13c284f1a1","tid":1185816,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b908548e02465145eb13c67de54abe30964f255d","tid":1185816,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"用國族情懷去做道徳綁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}